# Hermes Agent version this build of Talaria is developed and tested against.
#
# Upstream (NousResearch/hermes-agent) does not guarantee API stability, and
# Talaria depends on undocumented surfaces — the Sessions API SSE event
# taxonomy, the /api/sessions response shape, and the models-shim's hermes_cli
# imports. A silent upstream change breaks those with no compile error.
#
# Record the upstream commit here whenever chat, sessions, or model switching
# is verified end-to-end against a running host, and include this value in bug
# reports. If you cannot determine the upstream SHA, record the version string
# from `hermes --version` instead and say so.
#
# Format: one line, `sha=<commit>` or `version=<string>`, then the date verified.

